				></span>
			</button>
			<button class="relative group p-2 hover:cursor-pointer">
				Give a look to my blog
				<span
					class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-[2px] bg-white transform scale-x-0 transition-transform duration-300 origin-center group-hover:scale-x-100"
				></span>
